OL,7,FThe Tories and Labour are focusing on
OL,8,Fkey economic policies today, with the
OL,9,Fformer appealing to pensioners and the
OL,10,Flatter hoping to cut through with
OL,11,FBritish executives.
OL,13,FMs Reeves today said Labour was now
OL,14,F"the natural party of British
OL,15,Fbusiness" and promised to lead "the
OL,16,Fmost pro-growth, pro-business
OL,17,FTreasury" in the UK's history, adding
OL,18,Fthat corporation tax would be capped
OL,19,Fat its current level under a Labour
OL,20,Fgovernment.
