OL,7,FMeanwhile, as he sought to get his
OL,8,Fcampaign back on track by offering a
OL,9,F#2.4 billion-a-year tax giveaway.
OL,11,FHe promised to increase the income tax
OL,12,Fpersonal allowance for pensioners,
OL,13,Fgiving them a tax cut worth around #95
OL,14,Fin 2025-26, rising to #275 in 2029-30.
OL,16,FIn her first major speech of the
OL,17,Fcampaign pitching herself as
OL,18,Fchancellor, Ms Reeves said her party's
OL,19,Fproposals meant there were "no
OL,20,Fadditional tax rises needed beyond the
OL,21,Fones I have set out".
