OL,7,FHer speech came after with 121
OL,8,Fexecutives, including the Wikipedia
OL,9,Ffounder, wrote to The Times on Tuesday
OL,10,Fto declare their support for the party.
OL,12,FStanding in front of two jet engines
OL,13,Fat Rolls Royce's plant in Derby on
OL,14,FTuesday, she said the increases
OL,15,Falready proposed include closing
OL,16,F"loopholes" in the windfall tax on oil
OL,17,Fand gas companies and the government's
OL,18,Fplans to tax non-doms, and making
OL,19,Fprivate schools subject to VAT.
