OL,7,FMs Reeves also hinted she would like
OL,8,Fto cut income tax and national
OL,9,Finsurance, but would not do so without
OL,10,Fbeing able to say how she would fund
OL,11,Fthose cuts.
OL,13,FMs Reeves said: "I know there is no
OL,14,Fpolicy that I can announce, no plan
OL,15,Fthat can be drawn up in Whitehall,
OL,16,Fthat will not be improved from
OL,17,Fengagement with business, and our
OL,18,Fmanifesto will bear the imprint of
OL,19,Fthat engagement."
