OL,8,Fdividing lines with the Conservatives,
OL,9,Fsaying her party would fight the
OL,10,Felection on the economy and blaming
OL,11,F"Tory instability" for Britain's
OL,12,Feconomic situation.
OL,14,FMs Reeves urged voters to "pass
OL,15,Fjudgement" on the Conservatives,
OL,16,Fsaying they had "failed on the
OL,17,Feconomy".
