OL,7,FAsked whether her support for business
OL,8,Fcame at the expense of supporting
OL,9,Fworkers, Ms Reeves insisted that
OL,10,FLabour was both pro-worker and pro-
OL,11,Fbusiness, "recognising that you can't
OL,12,Fbe one without the other".
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Labour hit out at the
OL,15,FTories' pension tax break, calling it
OL,16,Fa "desperate move" from a party which
OL,17,Fwas "torching" what was left of its
OL,18,Fclaims to economic credibility.
