OL,7,FThat would mean that both the state
OL,8,Fpension and the allowance ` the amount
OL,9,Fthat can be earned before being liable
OL,10,Fto income tax ` rising by inflation,
OL,11,Faverage wages or 2.5%, whichever is
OL,12,Fhighest.
OL,14,FThe announcement will guarantee in
OL,15,Flegislation that the pensioners'
OL,16,Fpersonal allowance will always be
OL,17,Fhigher than the level of the new state
OL,18,Fpension.
