OL,7,FThe policy will cost #2.4 billion a
OL,8,Fyear by 2029/30 and will be funded
OL,9,Fthrough the clamping down on tax
OL,10,Fdodgers ` the same pot of money which
OL,11,Fwill help pay for Mr Sunak's plan for
OL,12,Fnew mandatory national service for 18-
OL,13,Fyear-olds.
OL,15,FMr Sunak said: "Thanks to the
OL,16,FConservatives' triple lock, pensions
OL,17,Fhave risen by #900 this year and now
OL,18,Fwe will cut their taxes by around #100
OL,19,Fnext year.
