OL,7,F"This bold action demonstrates we are
OL,8,Fon the side of pensioners. The
OL,9,Falternative is Labour dragging
OL,10,Feveryone in receipt of the full state
OL,11,Fpension into income tax for the first
OL,12,Ftime in history."
OL,14,FBut experts have responded to the
OL,15,Fannouncement by highlighting that
OL,16,Fincreasing pensioners' personal
OL,17,Fallowance is a reversal of previous
OL,18,Fgovernment policy.
