OL,7,FThe former approach would have seen
OL,8,Fpensioners' income hit by "fiscal
OL,9,Fdrag", while the Institute for Fiscal
OL,10,FStudies (IFS) calculates that around
OL,11,Fhalf of the #2.4 billion annual cost
OL,12,Fof the new plan is the price of not
OL,13,Fcontinuing to raise income tax on
OL,14,Fpensioners.
OL,16,FInstitute for Fiscal Studies director
OL,17,FPaul Johnson said about half the cost
OL,18,Fof the plan was from not imposing
OL,19,Fthree more years of frozen personal
OL,20,Fallowances on pensioners.
