OL,7,F"So the #100 'saving' next year is
OL,8,Fmostly just avoiding a #100 tax
OL,9,Fincrease, rather than an actual
OL,10,Fgiveaway," he said.
OL,12,FTorsten Bell, chief executive of the
OL,13,FResolution Foundation think tank which
OL,14,Ffocuses on living standards, said the
OL,15,Fsales pitch is about keeping those on
OL,16,Fbasic state pension out of tax, but
OL,17,Fthe "biggest beneficiaries of another
OL,18,Ftax system complication will largely
OL,19,Fbe better-off pensioner households".
